verbose_text: It is of note that in our study, Myd88 inhibited the expression of IFN-I, Mx and ISG56, which are well-known antiviral components, but had no effect on the expression of the inflammatory cytokines IL-1beta, IL-6 and TNF-alpha induced by poly (I : C).
evidence: expression of the inflammatory cytokines IL-1beta, IL-6 and TNF-alpha
